Likewise, the second energy center,

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:09.040
the so-called Swadhisthan Chakra

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:14.480
governs the activity
of the aortic plexus.

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:22.800
The aortic plexus is present
in front of the lower part of the aorta,

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:28.000
and through its branches,
it governs the functioning

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:32.480
of the pelvic viscera
or the pelvic organs,

