00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:46.320
that we should look upon
our entire system,

00:03:46.320 --> 00:03:50.960
all these seven
energy centers or chakras,

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:53.920
as well as the nervous system,
because the nervous system

00:03:53.920 --> 00:03:56.160
functions as one unit.

00:03:56.160 --> 00:03:58.000
It is not discrete.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:02.640
It has component parts to it,
but it still functions in harmony

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.600
in its governance.

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:12.320
So, that is the second energy center
and the corresponding plexus,

00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:16.720
which is the aortic plexus.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:21.520
Dr. Pradhan, it seems that
the Void may not be an energy center,

00:04:21.520 --> 00:04:24.480
as is depicted in the
human subtle system,

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:27.520
but do tell us about that
