00:33:58.720 --> 00:34:05.440
Shri Mataji: Let us see how the seeking
comes within us, from where?

00:34:09.440 --> 00:34:20.480
As shown here, there is a center
called as Nabhi chakra,

00:34:20.480 --> 00:34:25.440
which is here in the center,
Nabhi chakra,

00:34:31.389 --> 00:34:36.363
which is placed in our spinal cord,

00:34:42.160 --> 00:34:54.545
and manifests the solar plexus,
which is placed midway under your navel.

00:34:57.120 --> 00:35:03.920
This is the center that creates
the seeking within us.

00:35:04.720 --> 00:35:13.280
Seeking is only possible
when something is living.

00:35:15.280 --> 00:35:25.280
A little bit, if you understand
that a desire is created

00:35:25.280 --> 00:35:36.520
within a little animal called an amoeba
by giving him hunger.

00:35:37.520 --> 00:35:44.480
Just think of it. It has no brain;
it has just a small nucleus,

00:35:45.120 --> 00:35:51.040
but it can feel it is hungry.
It has to eat something to grow.

00:35:51.040 --> 00:36:04.440
It also knows it has to reproduce,
and then it starts seeking.

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:13.360
It also knows how to take the food in,
but it does not know how it digests.

00:36:15.848 --> 00:36:25.000
That part is not its job.
Even for us, just the same.

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:34.400
So, the seeking starts
in a little amoeba,

00:36:34.400 --> 00:36:39.040
and the whole evolution 
is based on that seeking,

00:36:39.040 --> 00:36:48.640
gradually improving and improving
the ways and means of seeking,

00:36:48.640 --> 00:36:54.640
while the desire is that
of food only, alone.

00:37:04.560 --> 00:37:07.920
Keep your eyes closed.

00:37:07.920 --> 00:37:12.800
First of all, please put your right hand
on your heart.

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:16.800
All the time the left hand is towards Me.

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:27.120
Now, here you have to say in your heart,
with all sincerity, Mother, am I the Spirit?

00:37:27.120 --> 00:37:29.760
Ask the question three times
in your heart.

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:33.870
This is a very fundamental question.

00:37:50.960 --> 00:37:59.120
Now bring the right hand
on to the left hand side of your stomach,

00:37:59.120 --> 00:38:03.040
in the upper part.

00:38:03.040 --> 00:38:04.400
Here press it.

00:38:04.400 --> 00:38:12.880
Now this is the center of your mastery,
your guidance, your guru Tattva, as they say.

00:38:12.880 --> 00:38:17.280
So ask a question,
Mother, am I my own master?

00:38:17.280 --> 00:38:19.600
This is the question to be asked
three times.

00:38:19.600 --> 00:38:25.431
Mother, am I my own master?

00:38:37.200 --> 00:38:45.360
Now bring your right hand down below
in the lower part of the abdomen.

00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:53.040
Now this is the center from which
all the Divine work is done,

00:38:53.040 --> 00:38:55.840
all the pure work is done.

00:38:55.840 --> 00:39:00.960
So to ask six times,
because this center has got six petals,

00:39:00.960 --> 00:39:06.640
Mother, please give me pure knowledge.

00:39:06.640 --> 00:39:09.840
Six times you just ask.

00:39:09.840 --> 00:39:15.071
As a result of this asking
the Kundalini starts getting awakened.

00:39:25.951 --> 00:39:30.720
Now to help the Kundalini to rise
you have to cooperate with Her.

00:39:30.720 --> 00:39:34.880
So please put your right hand
on the left hand side

00:39:34.880 --> 00:39:44.080
in the upper part of your abdomen
and press it on the stomach.

00:39:44.080 --> 00:39:49.760
Now here you have to say
with full confidence,

00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:56.480
to help the Kundalini to rise,
Mother, I am my own master.

00:39:56.480 --> 00:39:58.720
This you have to say ten times.

00:39:58.720 --> 00:40:01.760
These are the ten commandments
which you have to say,

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:06.495
that Mother, I am my own master.

00:40:42.880 --> 00:40:49.280
Now, ten times with full confidence.

00:40:50.240 --> 00:40:59.360
Now please raise your right hand
to your heart.

00:40:59.360 --> 00:41:06.240
Now here you have to say,
again with full confidence,

00:41:06.240 --> 00:41:08.640
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:41:08.640 --> 00:41:11.040
This is the truth, you are the Spirit.

00:41:11.040 --> 00:41:16.480
But you have to say with full confidence,
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:41:17.440 --> 00:41:21.236
This you have to say twelve times.

00:41:48.720 --> 00:41:55.840
Now one has to know
that God Almighty is the ocean of love.

00:41:55.840 --> 00:42:00.720
But above all He is the ocean
of forgiveness.

00:42:00.720 --> 00:42:02.560
So He forgives.

00:42:02.560 --> 00:42:05.200
Whatever wrong you do He forgives.

00:42:05.200 --> 00:42:12.880
So don't feel guilty
and put your right hand across

00:42:12.880 --> 00:42:21.360
on the left hand side in the corner
which is made by your neck and your shoulder.

00:42:21.360 --> 00:42:25.520
Now here you have to say
again with full confidence,

00:42:25.520 --> 00:42:29.280
sixteen times, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:42:29.280 --> 00:42:32.560
Please say it, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:42:32.560 --> 00:42:36.000
Sixteen times.

00:42:36.000 --> 00:42:39.363
I am not guilty at all.

00:42:39.363 --> 00:42:47.499
Please say it.

00:43:17.520 --> 00:43:27.040
Now raise your hand across on your forehead
and it's a very important center.

00:43:27.040 --> 00:43:37.840
Here you have to say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:43:37.840 --> 00:43:40.080
Please say it from your heart.

00:43:40.080 --> 00:43:42.160
How many times is not the point.

00:43:42.160 --> 00:43:46.560
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:43:46.560 --> 00:43:50.240
Now some would say
that it's very difficult to forgive.

00:43:50.240 --> 00:43:56.160
But it's a myth
that we do not forgive or we forgive.

00:43:56.160 --> 00:43:59.040
We do not do anything
in both the cases.

00:43:59.040 --> 00:44:03.040
But if we don't forgive
then we play into wrong hands.

00:44:03.040 --> 00:44:10.028
So please say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:44:17.440 --> 00:44:24.640
Now please take your hand on the back agnya,
the same center, on the back side of your head

00:44:24.640 --> 00:44:29.680
and allow your head to rest on it
and push it back a little bit.

00:44:30.480 --> 00:44:37.040
Now here you have to say
for your satisfaction,

00:44:37.040 --> 00:44:43.520
because you always feel guilty,
that, O Divine, if I have done anything wrong,

00:44:43.520 --> 00:44:46.830
please forgive me.

00:44:52.640 --> 00:45:01.040
Please forgive me, from your heart.

00:45:01.040 --> 00:45:07.600
Stretch your hand fully
and put your center of your palm

00:45:07.600 --> 00:45:16.400
on top of the fontanel bone area,
which was a very soft bone in your childhood.

00:45:16.400 --> 00:45:17.600
Press it hard.

00:45:17.600 --> 00:45:21.120
Press hard your scalp.

00:45:21.120 --> 00:45:27.360
Now you have to move it seven times
saying one thing, which you have to ask for,

00:45:27.360 --> 00:45:32.640
Mother, please give us My Self-realization,
because I cannot force on you.

00:45:32.640 --> 00:45:35.360
So you have to ask for it.

00:45:35.360 --> 00:45:43.920
Seven times press it hard
and move it seven times very hard.

00:45:43.920 --> 00:45:48.214
Slowly saying that.